        'title': 'The Signal and the Noise: Why So Many Predictions Fail - But Some Don\'t',
        'image_url': 'https://d.gr-assets.com/books/1355058876m/13588394.jpg',
        'small_image_url': 'https://d.gr-assets.com/books/1355058876s/13588394.jpg',
