        'title': 'Lead with a Story: A Guide to Crafting Business Narratives That Captivate, Convince, and Inspire',
        'image_url': 'https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/book/111x148-bcc042a9c91a29c1d680899eff700a03.png',
