        'title': 'The Art of the Start: The Time-Tested, Battle-Hardened Guide for Anyone Starting Anything',
        'image_url': 'https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/book/111x148-bcc042a9c91a29c1d680899eff700a03.png',
